# i decided to get started on the intial analysis portion of the program, starting with the event ids. i created a python script of event ids and their channels, severities, and their descriptions. 
#i decided to do this because i know evident ids are the easiest way to identify a artifact for malicious activity. So my plan is when you run the program 
# the program should upload all the files, and then return all the ones that are malicious. in the future i want it to get more specifc, 
# and you can ask it questions specficaly
# there are a total of 103 events, so i didnt include all of them in this file 

